# Local Deployment Values

This file is generated by `install.sh` from `templates/LOCAL-VALUES.md.tmpl` using values from `.env`.
It is intentionally ignored by git so your public repo can stay generic while your deployed host keeps local notes.

## Network

- Time zone: `__TZ__`
- Fitlet IP: `__FITLET_IP__`
- Gateway: `__EXPECTED_GATEWAY__`
- DNS: `__EXPECTED_DNS__`
- NTP: `__EXPECTED_NTP__`
- Torrent subnet: `__EXPECTED_SUBNET__`
- LAN test target: `__LAN_TEST_TARGET__`

## Service Endpoints

- qBittorrent Web UI: `http://__FITLET_IP__:__WEBUI_PORT__`
- qBittorrent listening port: `__TORRENTING_PORT__/tcp` and `__TORRENTING_PORT__/udp`

## Paths

- Project directory: `__PROJECT_DIR__`
- qBittorrent config: `__CONFIG_DIR__`
- Downloads directory: `__DOWNLOADS_DIR__`
